maze

Class Cell

  • java.lang.Object
    • maze.Cell
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MazeRunner

    public class Cell
extends java.lang.Object
    This Class is used as a component in a Maze. Each Cell has four Walls: Top, Right, Bottom, and Left.
    Author:
    Erick
